        "mission_title": "Our Mission",
        "mission_text": "<p>At Seoul Glow Lab, we believe skincare should be a ritual of self-care, not a source of confusion. We bridge the gap between Seoul's innovative beauty culture and accessible, everyday routines.</p><p>Every product we curate is tested by our team of skincare specialists, ensuring you get only the most effective, skin-loving formulations from Korea's most trusted brands.</p>",
