        "values_title": "What We Stand For",
        "values_desc": "The principles that guide everything we do",
        "founder_title": "The Heart Behind Seoul Glow Lab",
        "founder_text": "<p>Our founder's journey didn't start in Seoul — it started with real skin concerns, endless research, and a deep love for Korean skincare's gentle, results-driven approach. Later trips to Korea deepened that passion, from meeting indie founders to testing formulas firsthand.</p><p>Back in San Diego, she saw how overwhelming K-beauty could feel: too many options, confusing routines, and ingredient lists that didn't translate into everyday results. Yet beyond that, she noticed something missing — San Diego didn't have a space where people could learn, play, and experience these formulas together.</p><p>Seoul Glow Lab was created to change that. Curating proven products, partnering with indie Korean brands & building a community-driven space where skincare education meets connection and self-discovery.</p>",
